ydbc ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thy </div><div class="t m1916 xbc h2b y10a2 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be done &quot; in me in </div><div class="t m46f x71 h2b ydcf ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the earth. </div><div class="t m4e x74 h2e yf53 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m20b3 x4e h2e ybe0 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Our daily bread,&quot; </div><div class="t m275e x8b h2b yfd7 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual as well as physical. Man </div><div class="t mc38 x71 h2b yb8b ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thinks he must eat daily of physical food to maintain strength </div><div class="t m253a x71 h2b y9dd ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and vigor. Is not daily feeding upon the Word as necessary for </div><div class="t m1313 x71 h2b ye3c ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">moral strength and vigor? &quot;Manna from heaven falls fresh </div><div class="t m100e x71 h2b yd84 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">every eve&quot; for God&apos;s people now as well as anciently. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
